# =============================================================================
# FIRMWARE COMPILATION EXCLUSIONS
# =============================================================================
# The dev-docs/ directory IS tracked in git but should NOT be included
# in firmware compilation. This is handled by the build system, not .gitignore.
#
# DO NOT add dev-docs/ to .gitignore - it must be version controlled!
#
# Instead, ensure your platformio.ini or build configuration excludes:
#   - dev-docs/
#   - Any other documentation directories
#
# Example platformio.ini configuration:
#   [env:tdeck]
#   build_src_filter = +<*> -<../dev-docs/>
# =============================================================================

